ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectChambre de commerce de Bonaventure, Saint-Siméon, Saint-Elzéar CHANGE NAME / BOUNDARIES
PrecisApproval for the CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE DE BONAVENTURE, SAINT-SIMÉON, SAINT-ELZÉAR in Quebec (a) to change its name to the CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE MRC BONAVENTURE; and (b) to change the boundaries of its district to the territory of the MRC Bonaventure.
